data.title: Meet Ed Alstrom, the organist for the New York Yankees
data.meta_description: Did you know less than half of Major League ballparks have a live organist? What was once a staple of baseball has been phased out, but not at Yankee Stadium. CBS New York's Steve Overmyer spoke with the man whose passion takes him to two very different houses of worship.
